Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么 有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计还有点痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过幸好伤势没大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军方来正式委托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 总之今天先好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天出来的诊断结果不错的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}好漂亮～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛大人肯定又是第一了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白鸟...美由？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二年的选举
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.07,0:07:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当选了学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈当了副会长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛则当了书记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后聚集对我们三个忠实温顺的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结成了以学生会为名目的「白骑士」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快了 很快一切都要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得我做到这份上很不可思议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想感谢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你 我脱胎换骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天看上去都如此耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是正确的感情表现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 我会记住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到椅子那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来 那个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁 休想坏我好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了军方的委托太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不用顾及绘理的钱包而大展拳脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明从来就没有顾及过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 以后干什么都不用负责任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是 可以毫无顾忌地行动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能快速解决事件了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes！能解开谜底＆完美救出美少女们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 现在设备也万全了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？设备？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不过人家说「没有许可不准开枪」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然装上了就要开枪呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.14,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们啊 不洗澡就开不成会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用身心都坦诚相对的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:10:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来护卫都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们可以卷铺盖回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们能不能帮我照看那孩子啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来啊 绘理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在可以功成身退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想夺走我的神秘谜团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 就算老天放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真海绘理也不会放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 我明白了 把前面遮一遮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急速爬升
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说了也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 别乱来啊 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都大闹过一场了 竟然还若无其事地过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没事的话 就回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始上课了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再继续妨碍我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命不保哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 现在到哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到正上方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好高 好小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐步降低高度 开始进行探测
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军方还借了些拉风的「玩具」给我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 地底探测装置值多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 给我认真拍好啊 要清晰无码的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是在拍写真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是花怜 前往目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 学姐也开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 学姐 请多加小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟样子已经被人见过一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 因为我已经进行了完美的变装
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能控制 跟上次一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有一瞬间 但是操场有条发光的线般的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料泄漏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要关掉引擎迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫降？你降去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华平安着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 我这边继续执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼拜堂 操场 还有体育馆的地下有构造物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当有规模啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是设施 到底是用来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白了 就是巨型机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七神合体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好强大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在电视购物上买到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别认真说这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是巨型宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对了 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外星人在诱拐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是美少女失踪事件的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了调查这个星球的生态系统 美少女们才会被抓的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所看到的就是其中一种Cattle Mutilation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}(*Cattle Mutilation 牛只肢体被切除 多被认为是外星人进行的实验)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 神秘事件狂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异常？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那里没人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一只老鼠都没见到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且房间里面什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我也不知道啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去 就像是搬走了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊 没有地方破损
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长射击造成的弹痕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子老师强行闯入的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都消失得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不在礼拜堂的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去体育馆看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pink Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Silver Eagle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Pink Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行B计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我转接高雷准将阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往地下的入口...吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有的 就在某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.28,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不战斗就跑 很让人介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是陷阱...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要闯一闯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了 绘理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘理？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地下无法通信么...这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 蓝华 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了 这可不是到了地下就会被隔断的通信器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人为干扰么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华的联络中断了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.61,0:22:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一套嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为你们的同伴的话身体能力会得到强化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是有生体认证啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.95,0:24:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是那么的过激呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.37,0:24:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.85,0:24:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙船？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.71,0:24:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能来到这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.20,0:26:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了 死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.63,0:26:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要结束的 是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.84,0:26:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你 Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.66,0:26:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero？
